            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>in a large bowl with the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, the juice of half your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>orange[s] </strong>and your <strong>soy sauce</strong></p><p>Add 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> chicken thighs </strong>to the bowl<strong> </strong>and mix everything together – this is your <strong>marinated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
