        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush your <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>peanuts</strong> in the bag with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>cornflour</strong> and <strong>crushed peanuts</strong> to the <strong>marinated chicken</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up until the chicken is well coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
