        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once the pan is very hot, add the <strong>coated chicken </strong>and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Transfer the<strong> </strong>chicken to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 10 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> Kung Pao-style chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
