    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>orange[s] </strong>into small pieces, discard the peel</p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot </strong>to a bowl with the<strong> shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> orange pieces</strong>, <strong>mayo</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> then mix well – this is your <strong>zingy slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
