      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to the chip tray, and return the tray to the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p><p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
